{
  "stem": "12904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But anyway, I became very much interested in Karl Marx while I was studying it in order to give the report, and felt that the premise to each according to his ability, you know, and to each according to his needs, that that was, I felt, a pretty sound theory.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was very deliberate that it was assigned, that the teacher assigned it to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--associated with communism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, one of my teachers, a woman teacher-- as I said, we called-- most of our teachers were called professors in high school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she taught literature, German literature.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is in my diary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She told us not to read the books that were written contemporary-- by contemporary writers because they were all under the Jewish influence.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even if the authors were not Jewish, they were written under the influence of Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was her theory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I realized how prejudiced she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she also-- my grades went down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had been pretty good, generally, also in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had also English and French, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I realized that the teachers, all the teachers I had, had become Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe they were Nazis before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe they were-- it was ingrained in them, you know, the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a lot of it in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But everybody had assumed that, after World War I, when so many Jewish men fought in the German army, that this would no longer be the case.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it, apparently, it was latent in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it still is, I believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so, then, of course, later, in '34, I was, you know, told that I was no longer wanted in school, actually.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's when I, you know, felt-- and I had been ostracized by everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
